
// This Hyperlambda code sends a signal using [sockets.signal] to a session specified by the expression [x:@.session]. It includes an [args] node that transmits a message, which is extracted from a JSON structure using the [json2lambda] conversion. The message content is specifically retrieved from the JSON path [*/choices/0/*/delta/*/content].
sockets.signal:x:@.session
   args
      message:x:@json2lambda/*/choices/0/*/delta/*/content
